@node "COPY" "SN Run v3.1 - Copyright/Registration"
@toc "MAIN"
┌──────────────────────────────────────┐
  SN Run v3.1 - Copyright/Registration
└──────────────────────────────────────┘

This software is subject to the "Standard Amiga FD-Software Copyright
Note".  It is MAILWARE as defined in paragraph 4s for non-programming
CNet SysOps.  For CNet SysOps who author their own software, it is
additionally defined as KEYWARE, meaning if the software requires
registration and/or a keyfile, you must "swap" registration with me.
(i.e. I give you a registered copy of MY software in exchange for a
registered copy of YOUR software.)  For more information, please read
the file, "AFD-COPYRIGHT" (Version 1 or higher), included in this
archive.

As defined in the AFD-COPYRIGHT, you are requested to send me a bit
of mail if you find use for this program.

Note that there is only one version of this program, not a special
one or uncrippled version for those who send me mail.  Also, this is
NOT a crippled version.  Updates, bug-fixes and further releases of
this program is dependent on the perceived need/usage of this program
as determined by the amount of mail I receive regarding it.

Please send all correspondence to the address below for snail mail:

